Use case label: UC03.01.03
Use Story: US03.01.03
Test case: testTextSearchFriendsInventory() in testBrowSearchFriend.java
Participating actor: Borrower, Friend
Goal : Be able to browse or search the DVD inventories of friends by text queries.
Tigger : Borrower click into one of his friends' inventory
Precondition: Borrower proposed a new trade with a seleted friend
Postcondition: Trades are pushed
Basic Flow:
    Borrower proposed a new trade with a selected friend
    System pushes trade online as soon as it gets connectivity
